00:44:47.539 --> 00:44:51.279
sees a big publicity poster, “Visit Kavai
[ph], you’ll have the holiday of your lifetime,

00:44:51.279 --> 00:44:57.170
blah, blah, honeymoon.” Then, he puts the
glasses on the wonderful colored picture,

00:44:57.170 --> 00:45:03.249
disappears, all he sees is the order; reproduce,
obey, enjoy, don't think, consume or something

00:45:03.249 --> 00:45:07.819
like this. Like, almost a Marxist dream, you
know, the glasses which tell you directly

00:45:07.819 --> 00:45:15.739
the social order. What's--I think that what
is--maybe even more interesting, the dysfunctioning

00:45:15.739 --> 00:45:24.170
which is actual today, because today as we
all know, we are addressed not only by publicity

00:45:24.170 --> 00:45:31.540
but even by ideology at the level of not do
your duty but enjoy, have a full spiritual

00:45:31.540 --> 00:45:36.420
life and so on, and so on. You must have noticed
this how--to put it in very simple terms,

00:45:36.420 --> 00:45:42.519
there were three big stages of publicity.
The original one is--let's call it, naively

00:45:42.519 --> 00:45:47.609
utilitarian publicity. You are solicited to
buy something because you need it and because

00:45:47.609 --> 00:45:52.200
of its quality. It's like you need a Land
Rover. Okay, publicity says it's the best

00:45:52.200 --> 00:45:58.589
car, it's the strongest, greatest space; it
doesn't spend a lot of gasoline, whatever.

00:45:58.589 --> 00:46:03.719
Then, we get this more consumerist publicity
which is keeping up with the Jones' status

00:46:03.719 --> 00:46:11.789
symbol. There they refer to what status we
give to you owning a Land Rover. It's not--you

00:46:11.789 --> 00:46:19.420
don't by because you really need it, you buy
to signal your social status. But that’s

00:46:19.420 --> 00:46:25.309
not all, I claim today precisely after 68,
we have different mode of publicity which

00:46:25.309 --> 00:46:34.989
is neither utilitarian, these are good qualities,
nor symbolic status but this typical “me”

00:46:34.989 --> 00:46:43.460
generation. They refer to your--the--to yourself,
to your potentials. The idea is buy Land Rover

00:46:43.460 --> 00:46:48.680
and you will realize your potentials, you
will feel free, you will feel authentic and

00:46:48.680 --> 00:46:53.680
so on. It's--as we all know, the experience.
And unfortunately, although, I'm very much

00:46:53.680 --> 00:47:03.209
for green topic, unfortunately, I claim that
even, that even with organic food and so on,

00:47:03.209 --> 00:47:08.880
let's be frank, it's mostly dead. Why do you
buy those rotten two times more expensive

00:47:08.880 --> 00:47:14.650
so called organic apples than the normal chemically
produced perfectly red or whatever apples.

00:47:14.650 --> 00:47:21.920
I don't think you really believe that it's
so much better for your health. I also don't

00:47:21.920 --> 00:47:26.730
think that it's a big, like, you don't boast
around, you see I have these staples. I think

00:47:26.730 --> 00:47:30.969
basically it's to make you feel good, you
know, and not just a stupid consumer or if

00:47:30.969 --> 00:47:36.799
it's endangered, I do something, I'm more
authentic, and so on, and so on. So, then,

00:47:36.799 --> 00:47:44.160
in these conditions the ideological injunction
