00:48:01.709 --> 00:48:08.109
on is as it were the bribery, like, what the
ideological text offers you between the lines,

00:48:08.109 --> 00:48:15.309
the obscene enjoyment and so on. For example,
let's imagine Nazi Germany, you look at it

00:48:15.309 --> 00:48:20.160
without glasses, the message is; sacrifice
yourself for your country, enough of decadence,

00:48:20.160 --> 00:48:26.579
of promiscuity, of Jewish immorality, do something
for your country, or use your terms, my country

00:48:26.579 --> 00:48:31.420
first and all that stuff. What do you get
when you put the glasses on? It says, "Do

00:48:31.420 --> 00:48:36.789
this, pretend to do this and we can have some
fun. We can beat the Jews. We can blah, blah,

00:48:36.789 --> 00:48:42.029
blah," you know, all the dirty obscene sights.
Wouldn't it be the same, let's say in the--in

00:48:42.029 --> 00:48:48.450
some nice small--nice, ironically, of course--town
in the American South, in the 20 surveys,

00:48:48.450 --> 00:48:54.279
the official message is Christian values and
so on, our country. Then, you put the glasses

00:48:54.279 --> 00:48:59.209
on and you see, "Do this and we in Ku Klux
Klan, you know, on weekend evening we can

00:48:59.209 --> 00:49:04.420
have some fun, raping some black girls, lynching
some guys and so on and so on." That's what

00:49:04.420 --> 00:49:11.140
always fascinated me. How beneath the official
message of sacrifice, duty for your nation

00:49:11.140 --> 00:49:16.859
or whatever, ideology always offers you, how
