01:01:01.049 --> 01:01:07.059
school is where you get serious education,
all sciences are covered, and there, we get

01:01:07.059 --> 01:01:14.679
philosophy. Unfortunately, Europe is now becoming
more like United States. But the reason, I'm

01:01:14.679 --> 01:01:21.459
an optimist here is that I think that what--when
I was interviewed, as it was kindly pointed

01:01:21.459 --> 01:01:28.630
out, I really think that now we need more
and more philosophy in the sense of delinquent

01:01:28.630 --> 01:01:33.259
problems, which if you want it or not are
philosophical, even the self problems that

01:01:33.259 --> 01:01:40.421
everybody of us confront. For example, problems
like abortion, brain biogenetics and so on,

01:01:40.421 --> 01:01:46.829
my god, to get an opinion on that, it's not
just an abstract question of ethics. You have

01:01:46.829 --> 01:01:52.599
implicitly to decide, "Are we free beings?
